rComments: Nicest person youll ever meet at UofT. Very approachable and very helpful. Great during office hours - he guides you through the problem solving process and helps you understand concepts instead of just giving you the answer. Also just a really cool and relatable guy.
Very nice prof, good at drawing...I would take other course offered by him if any.
Really good professor. Most people skipped his class but, he really stepped up his game after the first few weeks. Explained concepts thoroughly and was very approachable!
Fun person but as a starting prof he tends to go directly based off of the textbook and thus doesn't give any clearer simpler definitions to help you understand the material.
